reviewText: So many errors.  Once again this instructor references materials that have not yet been provided or forgets to provide the materials at all.  The quizzes can be hard to pass because there are sometimes so few questions that you have to get every single question right to get a passing grade or because way too much material has to be read to find the correct answer.  So much reading material is provided covering the same subjects but with slightly different information that it is hard to figure out which article will provide the correct answer.  Some of the quizzes provide no feedback so you can't even reference the correct article.After 5 out of 6 of the courses in this specialty, I learned that courses taught by Dr. Carter were going to be full of errors, omissions, too much reading (sometimes hundreds of pages for 1 particular lesson in a week, not for the entire week), quizzes with too few a number of questions, and overall extreme frustration due to the lack of support for students.

There are a lot of issues with sound in videos, the way information is delivered is not interesting. Peer-graded assignments waste a lot of time(up to 10 days), open end quiz questions sometimes make you spend time looking for the exact answer.
Muy completo, definitivamente toma un tiempo considerable poder terminar con esta unidad pero sin duda alguna vale la pena
This course helped me develop skills to successfully undertake, making use of budgeting and marketing.
bastante bueno e curso aprendi muchas cosas
gracias a los aliens que siempre confiaron en mi

It is a great course, which helps you develop the strategic plan of you brand step by step and takes into account all the areas necessary for it to be successful. I learned a lot and I am ready for the next course.
